==分佈及棲地==
[[File:Predicted_patterns_of_marine_mammal_species_richness.png|thumb]]（ 69種），C) [[鬚鯨小目|鬚鯨小目]]（14種），D) [[鰭足類|鰭足類]]（32），是1990年至1999年的資料<ref>{{cite journal|last=Kaschner|first=K.|last2=Tittensor|first2=D. P.|last3=Ready|first3=J.|last4=Gerrodette|first4=T.|last5=Worm|first5=B.|year=2011|title=Current and future patterns of global marine mammal biodiversity|journal=PLoS ONE|volume=6|issue=5|page=e19653|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0019653|bibcode=2011PLoSO...619653K|pmid=21625431|pmc=3100303}}</ref>]]

海洋哺乳動物分布在地球的各地，不過其分佈並不平均，和海洋的生產力分佈恰好重合<ref name="berta">{{cite book|last1=Berta|first1=A|last2=Sumich|first2=J. L.|year= 1999|title=Marine Mammals: Evolutionary Biology|url=https://archive.org/details/marinemammalsevo0000bert|chapter=Exploitation and conservation|location=San Diego|publisher=Academic Press|isbn=978-0-12-093225-2|oclc=42467530}}</ref>。物種最多的地方是在南緯及北緯40°附近。這對應海洋>[[初级生产|初级生产]]最多的地方，在[[北美洲|北美洲]]及[[南美洲|南美洲]]、[[非洲|非洲]]、[[亚洲|亚洲]]及[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]周圍。物種範圍依各物種而不同。平均來說，海洋哺乳動物的物種範圍大約小於五分之一個[[印度洋|印度洋]]<ref name="ship">{{Cite journal| doi = 10.1126/science.1165115| pmid = 18845749| url = http://www.felidae.org/KNOWELLPUBL/Schipper%20et%20al.%202008.pdf| title = The Status of the World's Land and Marine Mammals: Diversity, Threat, and Knowledge| journal = Science| volume = 322| issue = 5899| pages = 225–30| year = 2008| last1 = Schipper| first1 = J.| last2 = Chanson| first2 = J. S.| last3 = Chiozza| first3 = F.| last4 = Cox| first4 = N. A.| last5 = Hoffmann| first5 = M.| last6 = Katariya| first6 = V.| last7 = Lamoreux| first7 = J.| last8 = Rodrigues| first8 = A. S. L.| last9 = Stuart| first9 = S. N.| last10 = Temple| first10 = H. J.| last11 = Baillie| first11 = J.| last12 = Boitani| first12 = L.| last13 = Lacher| first13 = T. E.| last14 = Mittermeier| first14 = R. A.| last15 = Smith| first15 = A. T.| last16 = Absolon| first16 = D.| last17 = Aguiar| first17 = J. M.| last18 = Amori| first18 = G.| last19 = Bakkour| first19 = N.| last20 = Baldi| first20 = R.| last21 = Berridge| first21 = R. J.| last22 = Bielby| first22 = J.| last23 = Black| first23 = P. A.| last24 = Blanc| first24 = J. J.| last25 = Brooks| first25 = T. M.| last26 = Burton| first26 = J. A.| last27 = Butynski| first27 = T. M.| last28 = Catullo| first28 = G.| last29 = Chapman| first29 = R.| last30 = Cokeliss| first30 = Z.| display-authors = 29| bibcode = 2008Sci...322..225S| hdl = 1893/783| access-date = 2019-05-29| archive-date = 2019-09-11| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190911223329/http://www.felidae.org/KNOWELLPUBL/Schipper%20et%20al.%202008.pdf| dead-url = no}}{{open access}}</ref>。範圍大小的差異是各物種生態需求的不同，以及其適應不同環境能力的差異。海洋哺乳動物高度豐度的地區也恰好是{{link-en|人類對環境影響|human impact on the environment}}最顯著的地區，這也是科學家關注的議題之一<ref name="kasc">{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1371/journal.pone.0019653| pmid = 21625431| title = Current and Future Patterns of Global Marine Mammal Biodiversity| journal = PLoS ONE| volume = 6| issue = 5| pages = e19653| year = 2011| last1 = Kaschner | first1 = K. | last2 = Tittensor | first2 = D. P. | last3 = Ready | first3 = J. | last4 = Gerrodette | first4 = T. | last5 = Worm | first5 = B. | bibcode = 2011PLoSO...619653K | pmc=3100303}}</ref>。

大部份海洋哺乳動物（例如海豹和海獺）生活在海岸。不過海豹的陸地棲息區也不小，包括大陸及島嶼。在溫帶和熱帶地區，海豹可以離水生活，住在沙灘、[[卵石|卵石]]海灘、{{link-en|岩岸|rocky shore}}、[[沙洲|沙洲]]、[[泥灘|泥灘]]、[[潮池|潮池]]及[[海蝕洞|海蝕洞]]內。有些海豹也許住在人造的設施內，例如[[栈桥|栈桥]]、碼頭、[[浮标_(航路标识)|浮标]]及[[石油平台|石油平台]]。海豹也可能再近一步往陸地移動，住在沙丘或植被中，也有可能爬上懸崖<ref name=thepinnipeds>{{cite book|author=Riedman, M.|year=1990|title=The Pinnipeds: Seals, Sea Lions, and Walruses|url=https://archive.org/details/pinnipedssealsse0000ried_s7p5|publisher=University of California Press|location=Los Angeles|isbn=978-0-520-06497-3|oclc=19511610}}</ref>{{rp|96}}。大部份的鯨類生活在開放的海域中，[[抹香鲸|抹香鲸]]可能會潛在{{convert|-1000|to|-2500|ft|m}}的海底下去找食物<ref>{{cite book|ref=Whitehead|title=Sperm Whales: Social Evolution in the Ocean|url=https://archive.org/details/spermwhalessocia0000whit|author=Whitehead, H.|year=2003|page=[https://archive.org/details/spermwhalessocia0000whit/page/79 79]|isbn=978-0-226-89518-5|oclc=51242162|publisher=University of Chicago Press|location=Chicago}}</ref>。海牛生活在靠海岸的淺水水域，約在海平面下{{convert|30|ft|m}}，不過也會潛水到{{convert|-120|ft|m}}的海域尋找[[海草|海草]]<ref>{{cite book|last1=Marsh|first1=H.|last2=Eros|first2=Carole|last3=Hugues|first3=Joanna|last4=Penrose|first4=Helen|year=2002|url=https://portals.iucn.org/library/sites/library/files/documents/2002-001.pdf|title=Dugong: status reports and action plans for countries and territories|publisher=International Union for Conservation of Nature|isbn=978-92-807-2130-0|oclc=51040880|access-date=2019-06-03|archive-date=2016-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161007121143/https://portals.iucn.org/library/sites/library/files/documents/2002-001.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。海獺會生活在岩岸、[[海藻林|海藻林]]及有[[珊瑚礁|珊瑚礁]]的地區<ref>{{cite book|last1=Silverstein|first1=Alvin|last2=Silverstein|first2=Virginia|last3=Silverstein|first3=Robert|year=1995|title=The Sea Otter|url=https://archive.org/details/seaotter0000silv|location=Brookfield, Connecticut|publisher=The Millbrook Press, Inc.|isbn=978-1-56294-418-6|oclc= 30436543|page=[https://archive.org/details/seaotter0000silv/page/19 19]}}</ref>，不過也可以住在有浮冰的區域，或是沙质，泥质或粉质的区域<ref>{{cite book|last1=Kenyon|first1=Karl W.|year=1975|title=The Sea Otter in the Eastern Pacific Ocean|location= New York|publisher=Dover Publications|isbn=978-0-486-21346-0|oclc=1504461}}</ref>。

== 貢獻及研究 ==
由於海洋哺乳動物對氣候轉變的敏感程度很高，也是[[生態系統|生態系統]]裏面重要的成員，所以国际有不少科研机构和環保組織都对其进行研究。

